txt.en: You have caught sight of Sorzúr, a Lone Orc Hunter. His confidence in the marsh alone suggests he is a deadly and accomplished tracker.
The Lone Orc Hunter Sorzúr wanders alone through through the Dead Marshes, disdaining any path. \n\nYou were lucky to spy Sorzúr. Seize the opportunity and defeat him before he slips away.
A lone Orc prowls the lost paths of the Dead Marshes, fell and stealthy.
You have defeated the Lone Orc Hunter Sorzúr as he crept through the Dead Marshes, in service of the Enemy. The fell hunter became the prey.
